FROM [Blog] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Author] AS [a] ON [b].[AuthorId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [SVG] AS [s] ON [b].[Id] = [s].[BlogId]
LEFT JOIN [Paragraph] AS [p] ON [b].[Id] = [p].[BlogId]
LEFT JOIN [Rating] AS [r] ON [b].[Id] = [r].[BlogId]
LEFT JOIN [ProjectORBlogTechnology] AS [p0] ON [b].[Id] = [p0].[BlogId]
LEFT JOIN [Picture] AS [p1] ON [b].[Id] = [p1].[BlogId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id], [p].[Id], [r].[Id], [p0].[ProjectId], [p0].[TechnologyId]

FROM [Project] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Country] AS [c] ON [p].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Paragraph] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProjectId]
LEFT JOIN [ProjectORBlogTechnology] AS [p1] ON [p].[Id] = [p1].[ProjectId]
LEFT JOIN [Picture] AS [p2] ON [p].[Id] = [p2].[ProjectId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [p0].[Id], [p1].[ProjectId], [p1].[TechnologyId]

LEFT JOIN [SVG] AS [s] ON [b].[Id] = [s].[BlogId]
